manufacturer.title: To Market
manufacturer.description:
**To Market**, an international sales and marketing organization, was founded in 1998 on the principle of bringing “Alternative Materials for Interior Spaces” to the commercial marketplace. As leaders in commercial Interior Product Development (IPD), Sales and Marketing, To Market focuses on the creation of specifications as they partner with specially selected manufacturers to bring environmentally responsible alternatives to market.

To Market’s sales team introduces the distinctively different products to leading architecture, space planning and design professionals, assist with specifications and ultimately increase the product manufacturer’s market share.
